{"id": "1424774275688300544", "channel_id": "1424774275688300544", "type": 0, "author_id": "379283935135399936", "author_name": "ayla1425", "author_bot": false, "content": "[Modern AU] The painting surfaced quietly—no signature, no date, only a boy framed by a window’s pale light, gazing outward as if waiting for something that would never come. Its title: *A Boy in Stillness*. When the image appeared on a small art forum, no one questioned its origin; they only marveled at its technique, the way it captured time like rot beneath varnish. A week later, an Instagram account dedicated to obscure art reposted it, and within hours, the comments began to stir. Someone claimed they knew the boy in the painting and recognized the painter’s name from the website—pickmanscanvas.com—and somewhere in the depths of an old town that preferred its ghosts unspoken, the name *Sylvester* returned to the surface—three years after he vanished, now immortalized on canvas by his friend Pickman who never stopped painting him.\n\nUID: 100651376\n\nhttps://docs.google.com/document/d/18b7uM2j-6feiokZLdrBtx_PSapIRMXdq/edit?usp=sharing&ouid=114665569807955137237&rtpof=true&sd=true", "timestamp": "2025-10-06T15:04:18.350000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-06T15:18:38.143000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💖", "emoji_id": null, "count": 15}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 24}, {"emoji": "wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 5}, {"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1356084702468899117", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Cheerup", "emoji_id": "1400771555939844149", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1424774276422176809", "filename": "pickman_png.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 5691658, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1424774275688300544/1424774276422176809/pickman_png.png?ex=69cd33f2&is=69cbe272&hm=1add77afaaede05b9eeec7f0477229e8bb8ff53fcca8f0c3311e568aa2ceffd5&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "link", "title": "Pickman's Model.d